  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior Staff Nurse / Nurse Manager",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Based in clinic located at Orchard Road</p></li><li><p>Lead, supervise, mentor and roster the nursing team</p></li><li><p>Perform and oversee all clinical nursing duties including medication administration, IV cannulation/venipuncture, assisting in minor theatre procedures and cataract/day-surgery cases</p></li><li><p>Coordinate pre and post-operative nursing care for all surgical patients</p></li><li><p>Conduct patient counselling for all ophthalmic procedures; ensure informed consent process is thorough and well-documented</p></li><li><p>Plan, coordinate and maintain availability and sterility of instruments, equipment, consumables and emergency trolleys</p></li><li><p>Oversee stock management, regular stock-taking, expiry checks and procurement of medications, surgical supplies and contact lenses</p></li><li><p>Implement and monitor clinic infection control policies, JCI/ISO standards and MOH regulations</p></li><li><p>Conduct regular nursing audits, quality improvement projects and training sessions</p></li><li><p>Act as the key liaison between doctors, patients and external vendors</p></li><li><p>Handle patient feedback and clinical incidents; perform root-cause analysis when necessary</p></li><li><p>Step in to cover clinical duties during peak periods or staff shortages</p></li><li><p>Assist in onboarding and competency assessment of new nurses</p></li><li><p>Eye trained preferred</p></li></ul>",
