    "description": "<p>Aberdeen Eye Surgery is a established eye clinic located at Shaw Centre in Orchard.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The clinic has a focus on complex surgeries such as LASIK surgery, SMILE Surgery, cataract surgery, cornea and refractive surgery as well as other eye disease related surgeries, including a sub-speciality in aviation medicine.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>It also offers a comprehensive suite of services such as occupational eye screening services and pediatric eye treatments, among other services for eye conditions.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
